                     <interp inst="t17740413-33-verdict161" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               guilty of stealing the goods, but not in the dwelling house
            </rs>. <rs id="t17740413-33-punish162" type="punishmentDescription">
